Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:10.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}字幕转换助手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.90,0:00:03.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}流動的水沒有形狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.60,0:00:05.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}漂流的風找不到蹤迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.30,0:00:07.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}任何案件的推理都取決于心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.50,0:00:09.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}做了嫌疑犯的大叔一籌莫展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.20,0:00:11.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}最後可依賴的果然是這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}唯一看清真相的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.80,0:00:14.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}外表看似小孩 頭腦卻是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.60,0:00:16.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}他的名字就是名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}下榻在輕澤酒店的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.30,0:01:51.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}碰見了和律師同事一起出來玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.40,0:01:53.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}蘭的媽媽妃英理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.10,0:01:55.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}那天晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.40,0:01:58.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}去找沒回來的叔叔的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.70,0:02:02.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在密室裏發現被殺害的律師准水律子小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.30,0:02:06.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而大叔正在那房間蒙頭大睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.10,0:02:12.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}當然大叔作爲重要參考人被警察帶走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.70,0:02:15.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而剩下的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.80,0:02:20.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}那麽媽媽不和爸爸一起走留在這裏是要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真傻呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.20,0:02:25.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我是考慮到你才和那家夥見面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.60,0:02:28.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}雖然剛開始是有些驚訝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.20,0:02:31.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}但是那家夥是不是個會殺人的人我還是知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.80,0:02:38.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}嫌疑犯 毛利小五郎（後篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.40,0:02:43.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不好意思 請幫我轉告錢會付的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.10,0:02:48.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}難道是律師間的付錢方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.60,0:02:54.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}被殺的准水小姐的確沒有和小林先生見過面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.30,0:02:58.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且我還沒有跟准水小姐提過小林先生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.20,0:03:00.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不可能會有金錢上的交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.00,0:03:02.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}這也是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.10,0:03:06.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}已決定幫忙官司的小林先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.50,0:03:10.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而他又提早和准水小姐聯系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.70,0:03:14.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}從鹽澤先生那裏聽說了准水小姐的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.30,0:03:16.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而打電話給她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.30,0:03:18.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}被扔在垃圾簍的便條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}還有服務生提供的證言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.40,0:03:25.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}都可以證明那兩人的確約好在明天二點見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.40,0:03:28.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}貼在門上的那張留言真讓人一頭霧水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.10,0:03:36.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你好像是在上一宗事件和有希子小姐在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.70,0:03:45.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這家夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.60,0:03:47.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}怪不得總覺得好像在哪裏見過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.40,0:03:49.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}群馬縣警局的呆頭警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.80,0:03:53.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麽回事 警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.60,0:03:55.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}這裏不是屬長野縣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但這裏是長野縣和群馬縣交界處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}這地方歸我們管
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.50,0:04:04.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}見過有希子和這孩子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.80,0:04:08.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對 雖然之後她的丈夫也來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.40,0:04:13.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不過案子被弄得我暈頭轉向真的很辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.10,0:04:14.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}特別是她的這個孩……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.40,0:04:17.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}孩……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.30,0:04:20.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}凶手是義房伯伯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.50,0:04:25.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}山村警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.10,0:04:38.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}太太 真遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.90,0:04:41.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}看來凶手還是你的丈夫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.50,0:04:48.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}從凶器的電話線上檢查出你丈夫的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.80,0:04:51.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而且 被人從門上的查看孔目擊到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.70,0:04:54.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}你丈夫移動受害者的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.10,0:04:57.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}凶手十之八九一定是你的丈夫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.00,0:05:02.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等等 剛才不是說過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.40,0:05:05.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}我丈夫手裏並沒有電話線的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他是名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.60,0:05:09.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}換而言之就是謀殺專家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}總會有不留下痕迹的方法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是他爲什麽要那樣做呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.40,0:05:19.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真正的動機恐怕是因爲事件吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.50,0:05:24.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}每天都面對案件的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}忽然自己也想嘗試一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.50,0:05:29.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真可怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}如果交給這呆頭辦的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.70,0:05:38.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}叔叔真的會被當作凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.20,0:05:40.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}我在門口那裏發現很奇怪的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看 這裏……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.50,0:05:49.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果是那條線的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.90,0:05:52.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}已經交給鑒證的人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.60,0:05:54.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.80,0:05:55.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}掉在地上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.80,0:06:01.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}連著鏈鎖的三厘米左右的細線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.60,0:06:06.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}和掉在旁邊的鏈鎖的碎片連在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.30,0:06:10.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麽仔細看過那鎖鏈的碎片了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.10,0:06:11.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}仔細看過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}那只有一截的鏈鎖的碎片上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.30,0:06:16.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}有奇怪的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.90,0:06:18.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.00,0:06:20.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.60,0:06:23.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}雖然密室的手法也大致明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.60,0:06:25.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.60,0:06:27.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}可是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.30,0:06:30.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}對 是證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.10,0:06:33.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}用電話線行凶的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.00,0:06:36.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}把叔叔的手提電話故意放在門邊的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.10,0:06:39.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}挂在門上那張留言的意圖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.70,0:06:42.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}還有凶手是誰都有線索了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.10,0:06:44.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但就是沒有證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.90,0:06:48.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}以前買給你的MD現在帶著嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.40,0:06:50.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}帶著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.60,0:06:51.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}先借給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.00,0:06:54.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}不聽音樂就無法思考問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.40,0:07:00.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而令人在意的是挂在門上那張奇怪的留言紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.80,0:07:03.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這MD機什麽也沒放進去呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.60,0:07:06.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麽會呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}等一下 那是錄音鍵來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對不起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.40,0:07:16.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我的MD因工作經常用來錄音所以搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.00,0:07:21.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.70,0:07:24.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}的確那張桌子的上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.60,0:07:28.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}的確 的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.50,0:07:39.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}所以那個人寫那張留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.10,0:07:45.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不可以的 亂動別人房裏的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.50,0:07:48.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是我肚子餓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.30,0:07:52.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看你人小鬼大 根本就是個小孩子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.90,0:07:55.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}人家的肚子都餓扁了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.50,0:07:59.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}真沒辦法 呆會就我去叫房間服務好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等一下 那麽說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.80,0:08:10.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}佐久君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.50,0:08:15.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}怎麽樣 那個人在警察局的情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.60,0:08:18.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那個 毛利先生當時喝得很醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.90,0:08:21.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}似乎記不起爲什麽會在她的房間裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.20,0:08:27.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警察也不太相信毛利先生就是殺人凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以也很困惑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.10,0:08:30.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}這樣呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}但是妃英理小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.50,0:08:35.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}凶手無疑就是毛利先生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.90,0:08:37.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}准水小姐被殺的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.70,0:08:40.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}是在裏面扣上門鏈鎖的密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.20,0:08:43.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}而且他還睡在房間裏的床上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.20,0:08:47.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還有行凶的方法也是問題之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.30,0:08:51.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果是被推倒後撞到什麽地方致死的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.80,0:08:53.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}倒可以被轉認爲誤殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.10,0:08:56.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}但她是被電話線勒死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.20,0:08:58.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這可是個不折不扣的殺人罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}如果是殺人罪加上強奸罪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:06.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}最少關9年或者是無期徒刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.40,0:09:09.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}說不定死刑也是可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.10,0:09:11.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等等 媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.00,0:09:15.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}你剛才不是說了嗎 凶手是另有其人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.60,0:09:18.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看來果然是我判斷錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.80,0:09:21.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麽 妃小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.50,0:09:22.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}還有什麽事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.90,0:09:26.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}有些問題怎麽也想不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.10,0:09:28.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}所以想聽聽你的意見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.90,0:09:31.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}佐久君不是刑事案件的專家嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以對這類事一定有獨到見解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.30,0:09:39.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}來 一起走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.10,0:09:39.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}妃小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.30,0:09:48.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}說起來那官司怎辦好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.50,0:09:53.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她擔當的那個工廠的官司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.60,0:09:56.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那要不要我來代她接了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.20,0:10:00.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不過我和她是不同 這不是我的專長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.80,0:10:04.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}能令雙方和解 已經是我的極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.80,0:10:10.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}不好意思 你可以先去她的房間嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.30,0:10:15.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她的房間是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.30,0:10:20.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.30,0:10:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是叔叔呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.60,0:10:29.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}小弟弟 就你一個人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.40,0:10:32.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}警探先生他們回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.70,0:10:34.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}倒是叔叔有什麽事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.90,0:10:38.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}英理小姐在說有話和我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.00,0:10:42.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那一定是在說那掉在房門外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.30,0:10:45.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}三厘米長的細線和門鏈的碎片吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.00,0:10:48.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}阿姨說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.60,0:10:49.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}只要有那條細線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.80,0:10:53.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}就算在門外也可以把房間設計成密室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.80,0:10:55.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麽可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.80,0:11:00.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我可是把那加了鏈鎖的房門用力撞開後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才進到裏面的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.00,0:11:06.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}這麽短的細線怎麽可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果門鏈是本來就斷了的話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.30,0:11:14.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果把那斷了的門鏈的接口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}用細線連接在一起的話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.20,0:11:24.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而用細線連接的部分和連鎖的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.90,0:11:28.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}剛好是在開門的時候隱藏在門後的話呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.30,0:11:31.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麽樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.50,0:11:36.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.40,0:11:40.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}而且如果強硬地推門 細線就會斷開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.40,0:11:43.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}門鏈也會一下子分成兩斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.50,0:11:44.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你爲了不引起我們懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.90,0:11:49.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}就故意使盡全力把門撞開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是這樣嗎 佐久君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.40,0:12:03.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你對門鏈做過細工呢 佐久君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.50,0:12:05.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}在說什麽呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.50,0:12:10.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}要是被房間裏的毛利先生把鏈鎖解開的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.60,0:12:14.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}連鎖鏈的線在斷之前早就散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.60,0:12:17.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以才把電話線當作凶器使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.30,0:12:18.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}讓電話接不通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.00,0:12:22.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}有意把我丈夫的手提電話從床上放到門邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.60,0:12:26.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}並且在門外挂上請勿打擾的牌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.80,0:12:29.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是不想讓人來打擾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.60,0:12:33.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}而把我那正在床上呼呼大睡的丈夫吵醒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.70,0:12:36.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有意把手提電話放在門邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}如果在門外打電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.20,0:12:42.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}就可以讓人知道我丈夫在房裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.40,0:12:46.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}雖然我有叫人去拿備用鑰匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.00,0:12:53.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那時候就算我不打電話 你也會打吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真不愧是妃小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.00,0:12:57.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}推理得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}但在這個案件中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.60,0:13:02.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}你不做毛利先生的辯護律師還是比較英明啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也沒有證據證明是我做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.10,0:13:08.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}而且也不會在你的不敗紀錄上留下汙點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.30,0:13:10.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}我並不刻意保持我的不敗紀錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.90,0:13:16.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}總有一天我會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.40,0:13:20.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不過很遺憾 神話將繼續下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因爲是你自己不打自招的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.70,0:13:27.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}從你進這房間的那一刻就說明你就是凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你很清楚呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.00,0:13:32.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}這裏就是她的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.00,0:13:34.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這當然知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.00,0:13:38.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}因爲房間門前有肉丁蔥頭蓋飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.50,0:13:42.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}肉丁蔥頭蓋飯又怎麽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.10,0:13:49.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}沒錯 恐怕在殺死准水小姐以後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.40,0:13:54.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}當你正把門鏈細工的時候有人按門鈴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你看到服務生正站在門外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.40,0:14:02.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}還有桌子上寫著“肉丁蔥頭”2的便條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.20,0:14:07.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以你就憤怒地將便條撕掉扔到垃圾桶裏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.50,0:14:10.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}心想竟然這種時候還叫肉丁蔥頭蓋飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.10,0:14:15.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你爲了不讓服務生再來 讓他斷了這個念頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.60,0:14:18.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以你就寫了“我會付錢的 請把它退掉”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.80,0:14:20.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這樣意思的便條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.60,0:14:23.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}把便條貼在“請勿打擾”的牌子挂在門外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.20,0:14:25.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果不是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.50,0:14:28.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}怎麽會從你口中聽到肉丁蔥頭蓋飯這個詞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那只是碰巧看到罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.90,0:14:33.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}因爲看到端著肉丁蔥頭蓋飯後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.60,0:14:36.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}服務生很爲難地站在她的房門外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.30,0:14:39.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}所以我想這裏就是她的房間吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.50,0:14:40.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.10,0:14:42.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}那留言上寫的卻是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.50,0:14:46.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}明天二點種和小林先生見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.00,0:14:53.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你看到便條和桌上的酒店服務菜單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.20,0:14:57.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}粗心大意把“小林”當作“肉丁蔥頭蓋飯”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.30,0:15:00.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}什麽肉丁蔥頭蓋飯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.60,0:15:05.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}其實我是看房間號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.60,0:15:07.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沒留意到嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.60,0:15:09.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.80,0:15:14.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}這房間的鏈鎖很漂亮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.30,0:15:20.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這是拜托酒店的人暫時借用給我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.50,0:15:23.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真的她的房間和這裏隔兩間房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.70,0:15:30.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是說 你之所以會踏入這房間的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.40,0:15:33.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}除了你就是凶手以外別無其他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.20,0:15:41.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對不起 設下這個圈套
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因爲對手是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.20,0:15:45.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}我覺得不是一般方法就能應付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.20,0:15:49.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}現在才發覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.70,0:15:53.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}如果與你爲敵真有種災難從天而降的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.60,0:15:57.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但你怎樣讓警察接受呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.90,0:16:00.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看我進這房間的只有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.20,0:16:04.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}要洗脫毛利君的罪名單憑你的口頭證明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看到的可不止我哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.10,0:16:09.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}難道是這個小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.30,0:16:12.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}不止我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}沒錯吧 警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.90,0:16:19.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 我也是看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.90,0:16:23.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}從對面房間門上的這個門洞 一清二楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.00,0:16:26.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是吧 各位同事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.10,0:16:28.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是 很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}從頭到尾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.90,0:16:34.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}兩人的言行都用攝象機拍下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.30,0:16:36.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原來這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.00,0:16:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}這全都是這孩子的主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.70,0:16:42.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.80,0:16:47.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}動機難道是她經手那件案子的判決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.60,0:16:52.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}控告那工廠的是我的親戚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.20,0:16:55.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎麽也不能讓她贏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.70,0:16:59.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}本來我打算用藥讓她昏睡後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.30,0:17:03.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}把房間設計成密室造成自殺事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.30,0:17:06.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但毛利君睡在她的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}想自殺的人當然不會讓男人在房裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.20,0:17:13.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也不會叫什麽肉丁蔥頭蓋飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.70,0:17:18.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就讓毛利先生成爲用電話線殺人的替罪羊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.00,0:17:23.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}因爲爲了贏官司己方的律師被殺死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}會影響法官的印象的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.30,0:17:30.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}雖然有背于法律的正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.20,0:17:32.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}本來也打算自首的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.10,0:17:36.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}但就算你殺了人也沒有證據啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.60,0:17:38.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.80,0:17:42.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}就是那把把門鏈弄開的鉗子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.80,0:17:46.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那種用途的鉗子在這裏只有一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.80,0:17:51.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}之後打算拿著那鉗去自首的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.90,0:17:57.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但准水小姐只不過是工作上的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.90,0:17:59.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爲什麽要殺死她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.90,0:18:04.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}她是爲了達到工作和生活上的目的才當律師的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.90,0:18:06.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}而你不會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.80,0:18:12.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}用一些見不得人的手段來打敗你的家夥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.80,0:18:14.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}無論如何不可饒恕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}爲了打敗我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.00,0:18:17.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.70,0:18:21.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}她故意把毛利君引入房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}可能也是因爲這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.30,0:18:25.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}怎麽會這樣 難道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.10,0:18:29.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}爲人家辯護一直是我們的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你真的很有魅力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.30,0:18:35.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}但你從不看旁人一眼也不讓人靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.00,0:18:40.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其實我也是意圖靠近你的男人之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.30,0:18:43.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是嗎 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.70,0:18:47.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}不過這樣一來 你的辯護就有轉機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.80,0:18:55.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可惜沒讓你親眼看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.30,0:18:57.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你太太的名推理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.60,0:18:59.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}真不愧專門對付壞人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.90,0:19:03.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}真正的法律界的皇後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.50,0:19:06.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那個時候你又在做什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.50,0:19:09.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}當她把凶手引向圈套時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.60,0:19:12.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我正隱藏在房間裏好好看著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.50,0:19:14.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}而且當兩人走在過道時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}你太太的手提電話響起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.50,0:19:17.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}而且 而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.70,0:19:20.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}當凶手踏進我們房間時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.00,0:19:22.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}我那時不知道有多興奮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}能親臨其境多好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那麽 那家夥現在在哪裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.50,0:19:33.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}看 在那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.90,0:19:35.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}那邊的桌子旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.00,0:19:41.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.40,0:19:44.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}幸運啊 來得正是時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.80,0:19:46.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那種氣氛難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.20,0:20:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}真抱歉 英理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.00,0:20:01.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}你一定要相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.80,0:20:04.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}多虧你幫我洗脫罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.90,0:20:10.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還有 蘭做的菜似乎越來越好吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.30,0:20:15.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不過總覺得沒你做得好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.20,0:20:16.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.60,0:20:22.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}請快點回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.80,0:20:24.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不會再吵架的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.10,0:20:33.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天是我們的結婚紀念日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.20,0:20:35.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}來得正是時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你聽到沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.50,0:20:50.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}沒什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.00,0:20:52.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}爸爸 媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.20,0:20:56.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麽什麽 兩個人說了些什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.10,0:20:58.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}沒什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.30,0:21:04.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}在謝謝法律界的女王爲她最愛的人洗脫了罪名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.40,0:21:09.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是最愛 而是最壞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.80,0:21:11.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.80,0:21:14.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}你不是最喜歡喝酒尋歡作樂嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.60,0:21:16.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}花心大蘿蔔的大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.80,0:21:19.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你說什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.30,0:21:20.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.20,0:21:22.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}對了 蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.60,0:21:27.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}這張盤 借我聽一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.90,0:21:32.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.00,0:21:36.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}走著瞧吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.20,0:21:40.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}真是的 爸爸是笨蛋笨蛋笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.10,0:23:13.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對了 請快點回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.50,0:23:16.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不會再吵架的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.10,0:23:21.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天是我們的結婚紀念日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.00,0:23:23.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}來得正是時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.80,0:23:30.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}對了 請快點回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.70,0:23:34.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}還沒完呢 說得這麽肉麻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.60,0:23:41.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}感冒了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.70,0:23:43.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.40,0:23:50.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這樣說來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.40,0:23:53.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}電車裏的大叔是被混入了毒藥的飲料殺掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.00,0:23:57.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這到底是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.20,0:23:59.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}在這村子裏七年前發生了什麽事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.90,0:24:09.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}這到底是怎麽回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.30,0:24:11.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}NEXT CONAN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.50,0:24:14.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}第十個乘客（前篇）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.30,0:24:18.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.60,0:24:20.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}塑料瓶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.70,0:24:22.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}下回是在公交車上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.20,0:24:23.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}就是那個用繩子捆著的很好吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.90,0:24:25.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}那是剃骨火腿
